name: Red Feather Fan
desc:
Use this to increase Gliding Movement SPD by 30% for 30s.

This item possesses some sort of mysterious power. In the hands of the tengu warriors, it can have various effects, but in the hands of an ordinary person, it can still have enough power to "make one's body lighter" while in mid-air.

value.name: Red Feather Fan
value.desc:
Ineffable Breeze: Red Feather Fan

Legend has it that this fan is capable of unleashing various effects in the hands of a tengu warrior.

But in the hands of an ordinary person, it only possesses the power to "make one's body lighter."

Even so, this degree of power is more than useful for the average individual.
